En: Your belongings lie scattered across the field...

Ko: 검을 쥔 손끝에 아직 온기가 남아 있습니다
En: The warmth of your blade still lingers...
Your vision fades... and a familiar voice calls...

Ko: 누가 그랬던것 같은데.. 세상은 잔혹하다고\n 그런데.. 난 아름답진 않은 것 같더라;;
En: The world is cruel... but to me{COMMA} it's never been beautiful.

Ko: 잠시 숨을 고르자. 아직 끝난 게 아니야
En: Catch your breath. This is not the end.

column6: Your soul reforms... and rises once more.

En: You were supposed to roll{COMMA} not *tank* it.
Even the NPCs will talk behind your back.
Your elixir? Spilled and wasted. Like your potential.
Thy dodge key... didst thou forget it?
Do not blame the sacred camera angle.

Ko: 이건 어쩔 수 없었다고 합리화 중…
